{"tid":243200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢個世界仲可以有啲咩節日","createTime":"2017-05-14T13:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T14:35:49.000Z","uid":68711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a375f8b59e5416e9f65bc1636259fbfc197ce2","tid":243200,"uid":68711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"現時既節日 存在通常有兩個原因<br />\n1. 紀念<br />\n2. 促進消費<br />\n<br />\n父親節母親節我都算<br />\n紀念下老豆老母<br />\n我屌你老味大6整個乜鳩光棍節<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">屌你依家無女仲唔夠慘咩仲要突登提</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多節日根本就係商人諗出黎賺錢<br />\n大家仲諗到啲咩節日會出現？"},{"pid":"e4acdfa257c87fe346c1547361b904d8fe9e3f52","tid":243200,"uid":68711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}